		<a name="top" id="top"></a>
				<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">XEN</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Telecomix Crypto Munitions Bureau</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<p>XEN is a paravirtualizer, meaning that the guests kernels will often need to be modified to run on it. Paravirtualizing is a tiny bit faster than ordinary virtualization.
</p>
